523
00:21:40,375 --> 00:21:42,208
I'm gonna try to get
Restoration to back out,

524
00:21:42,244 --> 00:21:44,244
and either of these things
can work

525
00:21:44,279 --> 00:21:46,913
but only
if we don't tell Thomas.

526
00:21:46,949 --> 00:21:50,483
