00:41:30,627 --> 00:41:33,828
I have faith in

1017
00:41:33,863 --> 00:41:35,596
it's you.

1018
00:41:36,039 --> 00:41:38,506
But the clock was striking
midnight and I had to make

1019
00:41:38,541 --> 00:41:40,808
a choice
and it is just a client.

